  Lines:
  - SpeakerName: Lilith
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: "That was... satisfying. I've missed our little dances. My power is yours
      once more, Sovereign... as is everything else."
    PortraitOnLeft: 1
    EventID: 
  - SpeakerName: Hecatina
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: "The unsealing is complete. Lilith is with us once more."
    PortraitOnLeft: 0
    EventID: 
  - SpeakerName: Hecatina
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: "Come, My Sovereign. We have what we came for. Our journey back is long, but necessary."
    PortraitOnLeft: 0
    EventID: 
  - SpeakerName: Hecatina
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: "On our way back from the tomb... the kingdom, your kingdom, awaits."
    PortraitOnLeft: 0
